maine gandhi ko nahin mara ( translated as i did not kill gandhi ) is a 2005 indian drama film , directed by jahnu barua and produced by anupam kher .   the film stars anupam kher and urmila matondkar in lead roles .   in the film , a poem by noted hindi poet , sr . bachchan , himmat karne walon ki har nahi hoti ( those who have courage never fail ) was depicted as the favorite poem of the main character .